title: New Mexico woman ID'd as victim in fatal southern Colorado crash
text:
Published By: Denver Post - Today 
The Colorado State Patrol says a 26-year-old New Mexico woman was killed Wednesday afternoon in a single-vehicle, San Luis Valley wreck....
